snippet.title: Songbird Symphony Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out Birb in his musical quest through the forest to find where he truly belongs in this first trailer for Songbird Symphony!

Try the game's first prototype:
https://joysteak.itch.io/songbird-symphony

Follow the game's progress via our social media channels:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/songbirdsymphony/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/songbirdsymph
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/joysteakstudios/
Tumblr: http://joysteak.tumblr.com/

Join our community Discord server: https://discord.gg/CxgYMuA

Support the game's development: https://www.patreon.com/joysteak
